Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:21.27,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,130)}迴盪之音·拂曉之鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:14.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是去米斯托拉爾啊 真夠嗆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:29.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那邊飯菜又好吃 美人又多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:35.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休戰差不多半年了 還好我們活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:38.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:43.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臥槽 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分你個戰利品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:53.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:58.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此貴重的物品 我擔當不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 中士長官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:06.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 據說親待下喇叭手 撤退喇叭能聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都不徵兵了 真少見有新兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報名來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:15.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我來學音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:21.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真老實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:22.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵 你什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:29.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 下屬名字叫空深彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽茲今天是節日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:42.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節日？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:45.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能送到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:56.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 你的分配地 通稱「報時要塞」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著那裡走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:05:59.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授令 空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:11.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令分配到特魯瓦州·賽茲 第1121小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾維西亞共和國陸軍總司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13:20 任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:44.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖與琉璃的城鎮 賽茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下 到任時間是15:00
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:56.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以演奏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:06.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認方向 確認時間 確認裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:50.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降G大調 美妙的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10圓25分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼漂亮的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:18.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸在節日中的小貓 朝著不著邊際的方向狂奔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:22.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒辦法 小貓就是愛亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野貓還好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧 那是只家貓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過又發現了一種美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:25.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 軍人 要塞的女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:29.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之少女 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:53.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:09:59.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:26.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼漂亮地被捲入了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你這樣子成何體統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多保重…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水溫怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來當了個肉靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你躲不開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:19.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 這染料干了就會褪色 不用擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:22.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面在搞節日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源於賽茲的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說 是個怎麼樣的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:34.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之少女守護城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這帳先記下 那邊的修理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西婭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個多管閒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:09.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢 真慢真慢真慢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還特地出來迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:15.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別焦急 慢慢等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你父親給你的禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降D大調
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您借我地方洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:36.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何我總是會迷路 但也因此才遇到這麼好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:40.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣 但在這裡可不要迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能聽得出這聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:07.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常清澈 令人懷念的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:13.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非…非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你想為了那東西去送死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個鈴鐺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:36.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:42.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:48.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:00.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:10.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鈴鐺…一定是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:11.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:18.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:41.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久之前 非常遙遠的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:48.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這城鎮的谷底曾住著長翅膀的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:16:00.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔口噴焰火 震撼大地 使人們陷於苦難之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:06.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 拐走了住在要塞的少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她們困在地下的迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:25.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是少女們沒有放棄 用上帝賜予的金角笛互相呼應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:37.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃脫迷宮後 借助巨大蜘蛛的力量打倒惡魔並取下其首級
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:42.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 其首卻猛烈噴火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:47.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此下去 上方的城鎮將會被燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:55.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女們為了壓制住火焰 輪流懷抱惡魔之首
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:17:02.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民們每天往燃燒的惡魔之首與少女們潑水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:06.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此經過一年 火終於熄滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:10.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後 為了安撫拯救村莊的少女們的亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便設立了「潑水節」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人 還是沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:16.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管她呢 隊長快看 梨旺前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的跟她非常相稱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給她辦 果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是抽籤…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時迷路會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:58.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是因為可以遇到不認識的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:04.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:06.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想見媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:17.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 只要你祈願著 你的心情一定會傳達到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:18.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 聲音定會迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定會迴盪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:27.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定會迴盪著…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之少女 沉睡於此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:40.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷抱惡魔 平息詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願惡魔永無覺醒之日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:46.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:48.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金角笛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是惡魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:08.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達出去吧 誰來接收我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:29.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音迴盪 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:36.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我起來 空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:48.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要睡到什麼時候 這裡是「報時要塞」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1121小隊的駐紮地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:12.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 那個… 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:15.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:22.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑而已 但你別再勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了個這樣的鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:48.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:54.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這個要塞叫做「報時要塞」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:08.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宮梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:11.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:15.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來指導喇叭手的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:19.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.35,0:23:20.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺軍士長長官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:21.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我梨旺就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:23.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西婭…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:29.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長的方針 這裡無軍階之分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 梨旺前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:38.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 馬上開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:40.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹個起床喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:24:00.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的姑娘真蹩腳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
